    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《军火贸易大亨：坦克》是一款模拟经营游戏，你将管理一家新生的小型军火贸易公司，专门建造并向世界各地销售坦克。研究、设计、生产、出售顶级战争机器，塑造坦克的历史，从坦克的黎明直到现代。你的每个设计决策都将接受从小规模冲突到世界大战的实战检验，每项业务都会影响你的公司，改变世界历史。扩张你的军火贸易帝国，垄断市场，证明自己是当之无愧的军火大亨和坦克设计师！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>路线图</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >路线图上的项目是最接近抢先体验发行期的部分，当然，它们也会因玩家反馈、新的优先事项或不可预见的情况而变化，但我们将会尽力完成！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1662210/extras/18eb0671ca0f286b270e0c304c25cee0.avif?t=1762918675\" width=616 height=1033 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>坦克设计</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >重现世界知名的坦克型号或用各种部件设计你自己的独特战车，利用各种改进，使你的坦克适应新的挑战和环境。通过强大的升级包和现代化延长坦克的寿命！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1662210/extras/c367f60469119c7959be599c774222e9.poster.avif?t=1762918675\" width=616 height=326 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1662210/extras/c367f60469119c7959be599c774222e9.webm?t=1762918675\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>试验场地</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >直接进入坦克驾驶舱，测试你的设计方案！在障碍物中穿行，使用坦克的武器，探索整个试验场，尽情享受你的钢铁猛兽。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1662210/extras/d68d89918876a811ff5ab0c84763629b.poster.avif?t=1762918675\" width=616 height=326 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1662210/extras/d68d89918876a811ff5ab0c84763629b.webm?t=1762918675\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>开发</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >利用改装微调坦克的各部件，应对即将到来的挑战。获取对手的坦克型号并逆向开发，得到稀有的坦克部件。利用各坦克学校的顶尖技术，创造世人前所未见的决战兵器！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1662210/extras/d139891c39a2d3dd047e0a528e063667.poster.avif?t=1762918675\" width=616 height=326 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1662210/extras/d139891c39a2d3dd047e0a528e063667.webm?t=1762918675\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>坦克学校</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >踏上全球知名坦克设计师的旅程，将你的顶尖坦克销往世界各国。每个国家都有独特的坦克需求、军事学说、政治制度和资源储量。带领你的公司在冲突和世界大战的动荡中取得成功！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1662210/extras/e776acf38b45705a0cf8dcf1ddd55302.poster.avif?t=1762918675\" width=616 height=326 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1662210/extras/e776acf38b45705a0cf8dcf1ddd55302.webm?t=1762918675\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>公司</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >控制公司的各个方面，包括原材料采购、物流和员工管理。获得从建筑升级到新贸易协定等不同方面的提升，吸引并雇佣坦克梦想家来帮你管理公司的各部门！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1662210/extras/06cc05a90153cf2705e84d8288a94694.poster.avif?t=1762918675\" width=616 height=326 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1662210/extras/06cc05a90153cf2705e84d8288a94694.webm?t=1762918675\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>贸易和谈判</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >参加最能盈利的坦克竞标。提升公司的声望，在竞争中获得优势。参与复杂的贸易谈判，进行独家交易，成为世界上最强大的公司！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1662210/extras/d5247d943891008cb609f5d5674ec4c9.poster.avif?t=1762918675\" width=616 height=326 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1662210/extras/d5247d943891008cb609f5d5674ec4c9.webm?t=1762918675\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>冲突和世界大战</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >观察坦克在重大历史性冲突和世界大战中的表现。观察坦克的成败并根据获得的战斗报告做出设计决策。你可以制造一辆万金油战车，也可以根据具体战场定制坦克型号！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1662210/extras/79f8373f50aa6dd632215f4807eb18be.poster.avif?t=1762918675\" width=616 height=326 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1662210/extras/79f8373f50aa6dd632215f4807eb18be.webm?t=1762918675\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>当前内容</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《军火贸易大亨：坦克》正处于抢先体验阶段，这里有游戏中包含的内容列表。随着我们沿着路线图前进并逐渐为游戏添加更多功能，列表的内容一定会迅速增加！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1662210/extras/a645163f0a2ce72a124af29c19ea6c84.avif?t=1762918675\" width=616 height=492 /></span></p>",
